<div class="mw-translate-fuzzy">
'''Wydarzenie Świąteczne 2025''' to wydarzenie społecznościowe z okazji [[Wikipedia:Christmas_and_holiday_season|Świąt Bożego Narodzenia i świąt zimowych]] 2025 roku. W skład wydarzenia wchodzą oferty [[Special:MyLanguage/Shop|sklepu]] w motywach zimowych, kampania prezentowa oraz nagrody dla uczestników. Odbywa się ono w dniach od 8 grudnia 2025 do 1 stycznia 2026.
</div>

<span id="Holiday_Event"></span>
==Wydarzenie świąteczne==
[[File:HolidayEvent2025 VRC+Page.png|thumb|<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Holiday Event 2025 Menu Screenshot</span>]]
<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">The Holiday Event is a community gifting campaign for the holiday season.</span>

<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Users can participate and track progress by navigating to the Holiday Event tab in the VRC+ page on the Main Menu. By participating in the campaign, users earn several rewards, such as exclusive inventory content and a badge for completing the event.</span>

<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">The campaign began at 11:40PM UTC on December 8th, 2025 and ended at 7:59:59AM UTC on January 1st, 2026.</span>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
=== Results ===
After the event conclused, the final stats were:
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* 48,946 total participants
* 191,169 total gifts.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
The goal of 200,000 gifts was not met, however on January 2, VRChat announced that due to user confusion, about gift bundles being credited as a single gift instead of multiple, that they will count those gifts.<ref> "Regarding the Holiday Event 2025:", https://x.com/VRChat/status/2007133663297782053.</ref> In doing so, the goal of 200,000 gifts was reached and surpassed, resulting in the "Winter Cheerizer" item being awarded.
</div>

===Tablica wyników===
<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Users that have participated in the event by gifting can appear on the top gifters leaderboard. The "2025 Holiday Heros" leaderboard section is spilt up between global and friends. Both lists will show the top 10 gifters, and the top three users will have different stages of holiday wreaths applied to their profile picture.</span>

<span lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">Users can choose to "Appear as Anonymous" to anonymize their username appearing on the global and friends list.</span>

